          <sec id="Chlorzoxazone.Comment2">
            <title>Comment</title>
            <p>A young woman developed acute liver failure with an abrupt onset and progressive course 6 weeks after starting chlorzoxazone. Medical evaluation showed no other cause for the acute liver failure. Despite prompt discontinuation of the muscle relaxant, she had a rapidly progressive course.</p>
          </sec>
